{"tid":582853,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"狠炒4車長   九巴︰個別員工當值期間嚴重違規","createTime":"2018-03-06T13:38:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-06T17:31:52.000Z","uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"16be401d97961f35ef76c4e2a1e1020cfbe3d4bf","tid":582853,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T13:38:39.000Z","msg":"月薪車長大聯盟早前發起工業行動，九巴今日疑秋後算帳，解僱連同發起人葉蔚琳在內的4名車長。九巴發言人表示，就近日個別員工於當值期間的嚴重違規行為，有關員工於執行駕駛職務時，擅自離開工作崗位或停駛，對乘客安全構成威脅，亦對其他道路使用者產生危險。九巴採取紀律處分，並決定終止4名員工的僱傭關係。"},{"pid":"4a18da4146b402884bfb79c1b1ffa7c3ad7b51ee","tid":582853,"uid":85819,"like":3,"dislike":17,"score":-14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T13:40:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"70b3fa624a66fe6cd525cafa681629a808b8cae8","tid":582853,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T13:41:56.000Z","msg":"炒左佢地咪自製更大麻煩"},{"pid":"0b807693bfea3b653ef3a5c08fc4a295a0d3cdc6","tid":582853,"uid":93986,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"70b3fa624a66fe6cd525cafa681629a808b8cae8","tid":582853,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T13:41:56.000Z","msg":"炒左佢地咪自製更大麻煩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T13:51:17.000Z","msg":"佢地手法係解決提出問題的人就是解決問題"},{"pid":"b18f9f83a988ca4071fdfc6018b6cd21e045cb27","tid":582853,"uid":49316,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"4a18da4146b402884bfb79c1b1ffa7c3ad7b51ee","tid":582853,"uid":85819,"like":3,"dislike":17,"score":-14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T13:40:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T13:54:14.000Z","msg":"你條生癌五毛咁到有位幫支那吹簫<br />\n<br />\n含到雪雪聲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5c5981cb90f45350ef486ed574ddeb98bd71fcd","tid":582853,"uid":72280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T13:55:10.000Z","msg":"阿叔報夢話九龍灣二樓本星期會再下達聖旨<br />\n將會有更多人犠牲<br />\n包括不願意放棄更高人工轉職長工的兼職車長及帶頭係LCK 員工 what&rsquo;s app group 轉發支持訊息的滋事者<br />\n<br />